---
import AppLayout from "../../../layouts/AppLayout.astro";
---

<AppLayout
  title="Terms of Service - Tam Listen"
  description="Terms of service for Tam Listen."
>
  <main class="py-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1
        class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-8"
        style="
        background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #CEDA8E 70%, #97A859 100%);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      "
      >
        Terms of Service
      </h1>

      <p class="text-gray-400 mb-12">Effective date: March 14, 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Tam Listen is built by tambuzztam LLC. By downloading or using Tam
          Listen, you agree to these terms.
        </p>

        <h2
          class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-4"
          style="color: #CEDA8E;"
        >
          License
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          tambuzztam LLC grants you a personal, non-exclusive, non-transferable
          license to use Tam Listen on your Apple devices in accordance with
          these terms and Apple's App Store terms.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4" style="color: #CEDA8E;">
          Permitted Use
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          You may use Tam Listen for personal, lawful purposes only. You agree
          not to reverse engineer, modify, or redistribute the app.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4" style="color: #CEDA8E;">
          Cloud Services
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Tam Listen accesses cloud storage providers through the iOS Files
          picker only at your explicit request. Your use of those services is
          governed by their respective terms of service. We are not responsible
          for the availability or behavior of third-party services.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4" style="color: #CEDA8E;">
          No Warranty
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Tam Listen is provided "as is" without warranty of any kind. We make
          no guarantees about availability, accuracy, or fitness for a
          particular purpose.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4" style="color: #CEDA8E;">
          Limitation of Liability
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          To the fullest extent permitted by law, tambuzztam LLC shall not be
          liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising
          from your use of Tam Listen.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4" style="color: #CEDA8E;">
          Governing Law
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          These terms are governed by the laws of the State of Delaware.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4" style="color: #CEDA8E;">
          Changes to These Terms
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          We may update these terms from time to time. Changes will be posted
          here, and the effective date will reflect when changes were made.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4" style="color: #CEDA8E;">
          Contact
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          Questions? Reach us at <a
            href="mailto:support@tam.buzz"
            class="terms-link">support@tam.buzz</a
          >
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-white/10">
        <a
          href="/listen/"
          class="terms-link inline-flex items-center transition-colors"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-5 h-5 mr-2"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path>
          </svg>
          Back to Tam Listen
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</AppLayout>

<style>
  .terms-link {
    color: #ceda8e;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .terms-link:hover {
    color: #97a859;
  }
</style>
